\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Skip to 4 minutes and 23 seconds\cb1 \
}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf4 We've now completed drawing trend+season onto plot in green. If you look carefully, you'll see the original series in behind in grey. We'll go in and look at this more closely. Trend+season is almost, but not quite, recreating the original series. The residuals (in the bottom panel) are the difference between the original series and what trend+ season gives us. Here, the residual is adding are now, giving us the original series.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
