}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf4 But even this example, if we look very critically at what trend plus additive seasonal swing is giving, there's a slight suggestion that the swings are too wide at the left hand end where the series-trend is low. And not wide enough in the places where the series-trend is high.\
